@cherie.pune is a total vibe! 
From the dreamy interiors to the cozy corners and classy aesthetic, every detail feels thoughtfully curated. 
The food is delicious, the drinks are perfectly done, and the whole place has an effortlessly elegant charm.

Perfect for date nights, catch-ups, girl gang dinners or just treating yourself to a beautiful evening.🥂♥️

Tucked away in the heart of the city is a hidden gem that makes you want to keep it all to yourself. Surrounded by lush greenery, this spot has a calming energy that slows you down and makes you appreciate the little things. Every nook and cranny feels like a refreshing escape. From expertly crafted cocktails to delicious food that hits the spot, it’s an experience worth savoring. Your next brunch or dinner plans are sorted! 🌿✨🍴 

 📍Pimlico, Koregaon Park, Pune

Found a hidden slice of the Himalayas in Pune 🌿⛰️🫶🏻
If you’re craving authentic Himalayan flavours and soul soothing drinks, Yeti – The Himalayan Kitchen is the place to be.
From the cozy, mountain vibes to dishes that take your tastebuds on a trek , everything here makes you want to come back again (and again).
Trust me, this spot is a whole vibe.
Pune foodies, don’t miss out on this gem!

📍Yeti -The Himalayan Kitchen, Pune

Warning: One visit to Tipplr Bar and you’ll be emotionally attached. ♥️
Tipplr Bar is the kind of place that hits all the right notes. Cozy, stylish, and full of flavor. From dreamy plates to expertly crafted drinks, every detail is done right. Whether you’re catching up with friends or flying solo, the vibe is warm, relaxed, and effortlessly cool.

 📍Tipplr Bar, Pune

Girls night at Scout Lounge was everything ! great food, delicious cocktails and mocktails, and a vibe that made us want to stay all night. The seating and ambiance were super chill, the perfect spot to catch up and enjoy good company. So glad to celebrate with my bestie and make some fun memories!

Zeta by Hyatt Regency isn’t just dinner, it’s a dream woven in candlelight.✨ 
From the fire-kissed aroma of live pizzas to the soft serenade of live music, every moment is crafted to delight. Cozy corners, indulgent mocktails, and a finale of Tiramisu and Panna Cotta that lingers like a sweet memory. 🍷🎶 A place where every detail whispers elegance and every night feels unforgettable.
